---
title: Oven-Roasted Mediterranean Cauliflower with Bulgur, Tzatziki, and Chili Cumin Oil
description: Think cauliflower is forever destined to be a side dish? Think again. Roasting the creamy white vegetable transforms it into the star of the meal. In this recipe, it’s nestled between a creamy drizzle of tzatziki sauce and a bed of hearty bulgur. And don’t forget that the brassica is packed with calcium, magnesium, and vitamin C, making it as nutritious as it is delicious.
